  <div class="c-entry-hero__content l-segment l-feature">
    
    
    <h1 class="c-page-title">The case against killing Qassem Soleimani  </h1>

    <p class="c-entry-summary p-dek">Why Trump’s decision to target the Iranian military commander was a mistake, explained by an expert.</p>

    <div class="c-byline">
  <span class="c-byline-wrapper">
    
      
