<div class="c-entry-content ">
  <p id="jy6KKu"><em>This is the first of a two-part series examining the arguments for and against the Trump administration’s decision to kill Iranian Maj. Gen. Qassem Soleimani. Read the case for the targeting of Soleimani </em><a href="https://www.vox.com/world/2020/1/8/21055785/trump-iran-case-for-kill-qassem-soleimani"><em>here</em></a><em>.</em></p>
<p id="A6Y2LZ">Last Thursday, the Trump administration authorized a drone strike that killed <a href="https://www.vox.com/2020/1/2/21047655/iran-us-strike-general-qassem-soleimani-pentagon-news">Qassem Soleimani</a>, the head of Iran’s paramilitary forces and one of the most powerful men in the country.</p>
<p id="WtQyFN">The attack has ignited a debate about whether it was legal and worth the risk. Previous administrations had the opportunity to take out Soleimani <a href="https://www.businessinsider.com/why-neither-bush-or-obama-killed-iranian-general-qassem-soleimani-2020-1">and chose not to</a>, mostly because of concerns that it would lead to a series of dangerous escalations on both sides.</p>
<p id="7FRBmr">Prominent Republicans like <a href="https://www.msnbc.com/morning-joe/watch/congressman-explains-why-the-killing-of-soleimani-was-a-good-thing-76101189665">Texas Rep. Will Hurd</a> have defended the strike, claiming Soleimani had plenty of American blood on his hands and posed an immediate and continuing danger. </p>
<div class="c-wide-block">  <figure class="e-image">
  <span class="e-image__inner">
    
    <span class="e-image__image " data-original="https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/19571589/GettyImages_607574922.jpg">
      
        <picture class="c-picture" data-cid="site/picture_element-1593518839_5556_51589" data-cdata='{"asset_id":19571589,"ratio":"*"}'>
  


  <source srcset="https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/Xz14VRNeymsUvRF77YTKDZohph8=/0x0:2102x1401/320x0/filters:focal(0x0:2102x1401):format(webp):no_upscale()/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/19571589/GettyImages_607574922.jpg 320w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/8FxZW22KhB62nwt8T9jg_fZwUo8=/0x0:2102x1401/520x0/filters:focal(0x0:2102x1401):format(webp):no_upscale()/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/19571589/GettyImages_607574922.jpg 520w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/9KSwiQiW6hAzf-qGBhQoQ-ENsRY=/0x0:2102x1401/720x0/filters:focal(0x0:2102x1401):format(webp):no_upscale()/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/19571589/GettyImages_607574922.jpg 720w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/mqCB6-08jgmkUrPSVTrL1v1x__U=/0x0:2102x1401/920x0/filters:focal(0x0:2102x1401):format(webp):no_upscale()/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/19571589/GettyImages_607574922.jpg 920w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/JNB-bgcgpnzTPQqdTGHRNUBicO0=/0x0:2102x1401/1120x0/filters:focal(0x0:2102x1401):format(webp):no_upscale()/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/19571589/GettyImages_607574922.jpg 1120w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/3beOP7L4OI0XYjHbFW5kM4GdZcU=/0x0:2102x1401/1320x0/filters:focal(0x0:2102x1401):format(webp):no_upscale()/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/19571589/GettyImages_607574922.jpg 1320w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/ifRgrcGAZydor65XPQeAHK7y29A=/0x0:2102x1401/1520x0/filters:focal(0x0:2102x1401):format(webp):no_upscale()/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/19571589/GettyImages_607574922.jpg 1520w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/XjN-NoXgRTtbXWopOG2m69weMhw=/0x0:2102x1401/1720x0/filters:focal(0x0:2102x1401):format(webp):no_upscale()/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/19571589/GettyImages_607574922.jpg 1720w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/jOtMGaugzujl5ygiPGAV8Hrvsn0=/0x0:2102x1401/1920x0/filters:focal(0x0:2102x1401):format(webp):no_upscale()/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/19571589/GettyImages_607574922.jpg 1920w" sizes="90vw" type="image/webp">


<img srcset="https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/Rb8K5DNkT1sJkGiTdbEUCYNXKr4=/0x0:2102x1401/320x0/filters:focal(0x0:2102x1401):no_upscale()/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/19571589/GettyImages_607574922.jpg 320w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/4ShAwqfALS4rYWayJ38-R-E07rU=/0x0:2102x1401/520x0/filters:focal(0x0:2102x1401):no_upscale()/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/19571589/GettyImages_607574922.jpg 520w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/deJmBJEOoccY_ekmMS4NlZn1q8Y=/0x0:2102x1401/720x0/filters:focal(0x0:2102x1401):no_upscale()/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/19571589/GettyImages_607574922.jpg 720w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/UJ25Q-8qmYLNG8hH_TIk3ZGavWQ=/0x0:2102x1401/920x0/filters:focal(0x0:2102x1401):no_upscale()/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/19571589/GettyImages_607574922.jpg 920w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/W8YVOKmVOj9nP6Rql-Ia7-Nthno=/0x0:2102x1401/1120x0/filters:focal(0x0:2102x1401):no_upscale()/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/19571589/GettyImages_607574922.jpg 1120w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/1LaM_oaSPLh94d1XIxlDXVBgYoQ=/0x0:2102x1401/1320x0/filters:focal(0x0:2102x1401):no_upscale()/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/19571589/GettyImages_607574922.jpg 1320w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/jm6z8eu0q3qCf63ikGDs25SAIII=/0x0:2102x1401/1520x0/filters:focal(0x0:2102x1401):no_upscale()/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/19571589/GettyImages_607574922.jpg 1520w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/_2CHKdNfXuf8vqSW3VIkmJHYDjY=/0x0:2102x1401/1720x0/filters:focal(0x0:2102x1401):no_upscale()/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/19571589/GettyImages_607574922.jpg 1720w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/6XXRQjGLqAcKVILlUjvn-oowYQo=/0x0:2102x1401/1920x0/filters:focal(0x0:2102x1401):no_upscale()/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/19571589/GettyImages_607574922.jpg 1920w" sizes="90vw" alt="" data-upload-width="2102" src="https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/JITHZ_8K_xD1uWmCO5-0ecsdexI=/0x0:2102x140